headline.print_headline: Instant View: China Inflation Hovers Near Five-Year Low in October
headline.main: Instant View: China Inflation Hovers Near Five-Year Low in October

lead_paragraph: China's annual consumer inflation remained near a five-year low of 1.6 percent in October, unchanged from September and adding to concerns that domestic demand remains sluggish despite a raft of stimulus measures.
